    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二王子",
        "刘谌",
        "崔夫人",
        "董敏"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崔夫人抱婴孩上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "二黄慢三眼板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢三眼板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "恨贼人困成都十分危险，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "二黄慢三眼板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢三眼板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一旦间国事衰黎民不安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "二黄慢三眼板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢三眼板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "为什么这时候不见回还！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘谌 （内二黄导板） 怒冲冲离了皇宫院，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘谌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不由本爵咬牙关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "未曾进宫先拔剑"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这才是儿女情长英雄气短、我的两手酸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷呀，进得宫来，一语不发，为何仗剑就杀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妇道人家，不问也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王爷说哪里话来！有道是：国家有事，君臣商议；家中有事，夫妻商量。哪有"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丈夫有事，妻子不问的道理！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既是一定要问，对你实说了罢！只因邓艾兵困成都，父皇听信谗言，明日就要"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "开城投降，本爵欲殉国一死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来，妾请先死！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崔夫人将婴孩放桌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将娇儿放在御书案，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心中好似滚油煎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恩爱夫妻不团圆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崔夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崔夫人碰死。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见夫人染黄泉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "点点珠泪洒胸前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人哪……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘谌割崔夫人头。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "剑斩三岁小儿男！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘谌杀婴孩。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手提人头出宫院，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（董敏带二王子同上，与刘谌相遇。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见二子眼睁圆！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘谌拔剑砍二王子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "董敏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀王爷呀！为何一语不发，要杀二位殿下？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国破家亡，死了倒也干净！"
        },
        {
          "character": "二王子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父王要杀孩儿，容我们见母一面哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们要见母一面么！儿来看！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘谌手举人头，董敏、二王子同惊，同走圆场。刘谌杀王子甲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "董敏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀王爷呀！杀一位留一位，日后也好接续刘氏香烟！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，出宫去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "董敏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（董敏拉起王子乙同急出门，刘谌赶上，杀王子乙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "董敏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国破家亡，二位殿下已死，咱家也撞死了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（董敏碰死。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个忠心董太监，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "同殉国难美名传。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘谌割人头。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘谌",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祖庙之内祭祖先！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘谌提人头下。）"
        }
      ],
